  "version": "1",
  "_comment": "Flowork OS SOVEREIGN default router config. DEFAULT = Claude via the cloak (the user's OWN subscription/credentials — sovereign by account, no secret baked here, token resolved at runtime from claude_credentials). Local Qwen (Ollama 127.0.0.1:11434) stays as a lower-priority fallback so the appliance still works fully OFFLINE, and as an opt-in privacy tier (intentRouting routes 'local'-tagged/private prompts to it). Small local models hallucinate, so they are no longer the default. See docs/SOVEREIGN.md.",
